#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
#define ll long long
#define mod 10000
int main()
{
    ll t,n,i,ans,cal;
    scanf("%lld",&t);
    while(t--)
    {
        ans=1;
        scanf("%lld",&n);
        for(i=2;i<=sqrt(n);i++)
        {
            if(n%i==0)
            {
                cal=n/i;
                if(i!=cal)
                {
                    ans=(ans*i*cal)%mod;
                }
                else
                {
                    ans=(ans*i)%mod;
                }
            }
        }
        if(ans==0)
            printf("0000\n");
        else
            printf("%lld\n",ans);
    }
    return 0;
}
